/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   PUR3V4D3R IMPERIAL THEME
   Version: 1.0.0
   Author: Pur3v4d3r
   Description: Professional dark theme with red/grey/black palette

   Features:
   - Crimson (#E50000) accent throughout
   - Glassmorphism sidebars with backdrop blur
   - Advanced code blocks with dual borders
   - 30 essential callout types with Card Elevated style
   - Zero animations for maximum performance
   - No !important flags (clean CSS hierarchy)

   Color Palette:
   - Red: #E50000 (vivid), #FF0000 (bright), #B30000 (dark)
   - Grey: #E0E0E0 (bright), #A3A3A3 (medium), #7A7A7A (dark)
   - Black: #0A0A0A (deep), #121212 (base), #1E1E1E (raised)
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

